<h1>INTERNATIONAL COMMUNIST LEAGUE: WE SHARE THE PAIN OF THE PEOPLE OF ALL NATIONS WHO HAVE LOST THEIR LIVES DUE TO THE EARTHQUAKE IN TURKEY, ROJAVA AND NORTHERN SYRIA!</h1>
<p>Author: COMMUNIST INTERNATIONAL MARXIST-LENINIST-MAOIST ONLINE NEWSPAPER</p>
<p>Time: 2023-03-01T95:00:00-04:00</p>
